description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology with this stunning 2020 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR. This sleek and sophisticated sedan is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Boasting a premium package that includes:

2-way driver power lumbar
Heated Front Seats
Single Panel Moonroof
Heated Outside Mirrors
LED turn signal indicators

Elevate your commute with the SR Floor Mats/Trunk Mat/Hideaway Nets, adding a touch of refinement to your ride. The body-colored splash guards ensure a seamless, stylish appearance.

Under the hood, this Altima 2.5 SR is powered by a 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a CVT with Xtronic transmission, delivering an impressive 27 city/37 highway MPG. Experience the perfect balance of efficiency and performance.

Step into the modern cabin, where you'll find a wealth of advanced features, including NissanConnect with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, allowing you to stay connected on the go. The sport steering wheel and sport seat trim add a touch of sportiness, while the Blind Spot Warning and Rear Parking Sensors provide added peace of mind.

Designed with your safety in mind, this Altima 2.5 SR is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Automatic Emergency Braking, Intelligent Forward Collision Warning, and Intelligent Driver Alertness. Rest assured, you and your loved ones will be well-protected.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2020 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR. With its striking exterior, premium features, and impressive performance, this sedan is poised to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this Altima should be your next automotive companion.
